headline: Octane Earns a 2025 FICO Decision Award; Responsibly Expands Credit Access with FICO Auto Score 10
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., May 22, 2025--Global analytics software leader FICO today announced that Octane (Octane Lending, Inc.), the fintech revolutionizing the buying experience for major recreational purchases, earned a 2025 FICO® Decision Award for Customer Onboarding and Management. Since 2016, Octane has partnered with FICO to support its risk management and responsibly expand credit access.
